{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sort of-- you know, I don't know how I lived frankly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Joint subsidized us, you know, gave us money and-- for the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By this time, you see, it was Romania again, because the Hungarians were part of the Axis and the Romanians, they're very smart in switching in the last moment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, they were the great Russian allies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so there was the Kommandatura.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very much Russian-run, and the Romanians were nominally in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Communist party really took over, the Romanian Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, I went to-- it was some sort of a little drugstore that a friend of mine, a young man, opened, and we used to gather there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was sort of a [NON-ENGLISH] meaning a gathering, a watering hole, sort of, where the survivors would come and schmooze and chat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but before then, it-- we began doing something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night, we would go to somebody's home, gather together, and drink and get drunk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would sing songs that the Nazis would sing against us, the Hungarian Nazis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember one particular song.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would sing the melody, and the original song was saying something to the effect, [HUNGARIAN], 'one Jew, two Jews, we just hung the chief Jew,' something of that sort.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, we would take the melody and twist it around and sing, 'one Nazi, two Nazi, we just hung the chief Nazi.' But we would get drunk night after night, night after night.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow, this is how, you know, we spent our nights and in many-- many nights, we were in somebody else's house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were screaming it on the top of our lungs, on the top of our lungs to get it out, to get it out.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
